iati-activity.description:
Specific Objectives of the assignment are as follow:
i) to review the advancement of the decentralisation reform and main developments since the previous sector review;
ii) to assess the performance indicators matrix under the EU Sector Reform Contract and inform on the disbursement of the variable tranches; 
iii) to assess the alignment of the performance indicators matrix under the EU Sector Reform Contract with the existing elements of the monitoring framework

Promote good governance, especially accountability and local ownership, through increased applicability and effectiveness of the APRM process;
Improve social dialogue and networking between civil society organisations and decision-makers;
Contribute to national strategies on a more effective implementation of the APRM process.
